09:48.922 --> 09:51.222
Hey, wait. Shh, shh, shh.
It's your dad calling.

09:51.224 --> 09:52.891
Diane, you are a go.

09:52.893 --> 09:54.059
Are you ready?
Okay. Yes.
[ clears throat ]

09:54.061 --> 09:55.627
Okay. Go.
[ beep ]

09:55.629 --> 09:57.629
So<i> that</i> was
the center of the conflict

09:57.631 --> 09:59.798
Between malcolm x
and dr. King.

09:59.800 --> 10:02.033
Bow?
Oh, I'm sorry.

10:02.035 --> 10:04.002
I'm just busy passing on
the legacy, babe.

10:04.004 --> 10:05.337
How's it going
in your car?

10:05.339 --> 10:06.638
Terrible.

10:06.640 --> 10:08.974
We got pulled over
by a friendly cop,

10:08.976 --> 10:11.843
And junior still thinks
the world is a safe place.

10:11.845 --> 10:13.845
I'm glad that cop
didn't look in the trunk.

10:13.847 --> 10:15.981
[ breathes deeply ]
game over.

10:15.983 --> 10:18.016
20 to life.

10:18.018 --> 10:21.119
The world's different
from when you were growing up.

10:21.121 --> 10:22.954
There's no midday
dance shows on,

10:22.956 --> 10:25.991
Nobody irons their jeans,
and some cops are okay.

10:25.993 --> 10:29.094
You're not just teaching him
about intolerance?

10:29.096 --> 10:30.929
You're actually
seeking it out?

10:30.931 --> 10:33.932
Yes, because I actually care
about the boy.

10:33.934 --> 10:35.934
Okay,
goodbye, lunatic!

10:35.936 --> 10:37.168
[ beep ]
uh --

10:37.170 --> 10:38.803
Ready?
♪<i> ...Treble</i> ♪

10:38.805 --> 10:42.774
♪ I'm all about that bass,
'bout that bass, no treble ♪

10:42.776 --> 10:45.710
♪ I'm all about that bass,
'bout that bass, no treble ♪

